column11: Note: Areas are included in this table if they exceed the stated threshold at any point in the time series. The April 1, 2010 Population Estimates base reflects changes to the 2010 Census population from the Boundary and Annexation Survey (BAS) and other geographic program revisions.  It does not reflect changes from the Count Question Resolution program.  All geographic boundaries for the 2011 population estimates series are defined as of January 1, 2011. An "(X)" in the 2010 Census field indicates a locality that was formed or incorporated after the 2010 Census. Additional information on these localities can be found in the Geographic Change Notes (see http://www.census.gov/popest/about/geo/changes.html).
